$(1)$ If the solution set of $f(x) > 0$ is $\{x|x < 1$ or $x > b\}$. Find $a$, $b$;

$(2)$ If $f(x) > 0$ holds for all $x \in \mathbb{R}$, find the range of values for $a$.

